snippet.title: Amber Heard HIRED, Gina Carno FIRED!? HOLLYWOOD is CRAZY!
snippet.description:
Gina Carano(fired) and Amber Heard(hired) have been some hot topics of the past few years/months. Heard for many obvious reasons, Carano for the same. Unfortunately, people like Heard seem to have a job, and prevail(somewhat) whereas Carano does not get the same treatment. Johnny Depp and Gina Carano are similar in some ways, and different in others. Depp was removed from projects, due to the fact that he was a "bad person" similar to how Gina Carano was treated. 
This is all ridiculous if you ask me.
